Terms of AP
Send Feedback
Write a program to print first x terms of the series 3N + 2 which are not multiples of 4.
Input format :
Integer x
Output format :
Terms of series (separated by space)
Constraints :
1 <= x <= 1,000
Sample Input 1 :
10
Sample Output 1 :
5 11 14 17 23 26 29 35 38 41
Sample Input 2 :
4
Sample Output 2 :
5 11 14 17




/*************************************************** SOLUTION *************************************************************************/





#include <iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
  int x,j;
  cin>>x;
  for(int N=1;N<10000;N++) {
       if(x!=0)
       {
          j=(3*N)+2;
           if(j%4!=0){
            cout<<j<<" ";
            x--;
           }
       }
      }
}
